OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy during the morning with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain. Sunny spells
OL,7,Fdeveloping in the afternoon as cloud
OL,8,Fbreaks up. Feeling warm in the
OL,9,Fafternoon sunshine. Winds mostly light.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FDry overnight with some cloud
OL,12,Faround to start the evening, but long
OL,13,Fclear spells soon developing through
OL,14,Fthe night. Mild with light winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FBecoming warm or very warm on
OL,17,FFriday with plenty of sunshine,
OL,18,Falthough this may turn hazy at times.
OL,19,FMild overnight with a risk of showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
